'''镜像宇宙'''，又称'''黑暗镜像'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bbs.flyine.net/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=238386&page=1#pid2762013 |title=与《黑暗镜像》有关的都在这里了，不过好像没看到有小说 |accessdate=2016-08-01 |author=xhzyzydr |date=2015-07-04 |publisher=飞翔·科幻网}}</ref>，是出现在《[[星际旅行|星际旅行]]》剧集中的虚构的[[平行宇宙|平行宇宙]]。这一宇宙类似《星际旅行》中其他独立于主宇宙的其他虚构的平行宇宙。<ref name="boingboing">{{cite web|last1=Granshaw|first1=Lisa|title=A look through Star Trek’s Mirror Universe|url=http://boingboing.net/2015/04/01/a-look-through-star-treks-m.html|website=Boing Boing|accessdate=8 June 2016|date=1 April 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Okuda|first1=Michael|last2=Denise|first2=Okuda|last3=Mirek|first3=Debbie|title=The Star Trek Encyclopedia: A Reference Guide to the Future|url=https://archive.org/details/startrekencycl00okud|date=1994|publisher=Pocket Books|location=New York|isbn=9780671886844}}</ref>镜像宇宙中的角色在性格上相较主宇宙富有侵略性、多疑、投机取巧。正如《星际旅行》主宇宙中描述了一个光明的未来，发源于地球的[[星际联邦|星际联邦]]重视和平、合作和探索，而镜像宇宙中人类主宰的地球帝国却热衷于征服。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Hantke|first1=Steffen|title=Star Trek's Mirror Universe Episodes and US Military Culture through the Eyes of the Other|journal=Science Fiction Studies|date=1 January 2014|volume=41|issue=3|pages=562–578|doi=10.5621/sciefictstud.41.3.0562|url=http://www.jstor.org/stable/10.5621/sciefictstud.41.3.0562|accessdate=8 June 2016}}</ref>镜像宇宙在《[[星际旅行：原初系列|星际旅行：原初系列]]》中出现1集，<ref>{{cite web|title=The Top 10 Original Star Trek Episodes|url=http://www.newsweek.com/newsweeks-top-10-star-trek-original-series-410044|website=Newsweek|accessdate=8 June 2016}}</ref>在《[[星际旅行：深空九号|星际旅行：深空九号]]》中出现5集，<ref name="wiredds9">{{cite web|last1=MacMillan|first1=Graeme|title=WIRED Binge-Watching Guide: Star Trek: Deep Space Nine|url=http://www.wired.com/2015/05/binge-guide-star-trek-ds9/|website=WIRED|accessdate=8 June 2016|date=13 May 2015}}</ref>在《[[星际旅行：进取号|星际旅行：进取号]]》中出现两集。<ref name="wiredent">{{cite web|last1=MacMillan|first1=Graeme|title=WIRED Binge-Watching Guide: Star Trek: Enterprise|url=http://www.wired.com/2015/07/binge-guide-star-trek-enterprise/|website=WIRED|accessdate=8 June 2016|date=29 July 2015}}</ref>最新的系列电视剧《[[星际迷航：发现号|星际迷航：发现号]]》后半部分也大幅涉及镜像宇宙。

镜像宇宙也出现在非正史的小说和电脑游戏中。镜像宇宙首次出现在《原初系列》的《{{TOS|Mirror, Mirror}}》一集中，并在此之后得名“镜像宇宙”。<ref name="tor">{{cite web|last1=DeCandido|first1=Kieith|title=Star Trek The Original Series Rewatch: “Mirror, Mirror”|url=http://www.tor.com/2015/12/29/star-trek-the-original-series-rewatch-mirror-mirror/|website=Tor.com|accessdate=8 June 2016|date=29 December 2015}}</ref>

